Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:56.89,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}如今奏响旅程的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:01.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,800)}{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}将愿望传播至彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:13.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}无形的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}若能渗透于月光之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:22.08,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.15}是你心中的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:26.00,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}如今 随风飘逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.68,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}明天就试着展翅高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:35.51,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}就如曾经你所期望的那般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:41.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}你能听到吗 那光辉的梦想
